  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à PCManFM</title>

    <para>
      The <application>PCManFM</application> package contains an extremly fast,
      lightweight, yet feature-rich file manager with tabbed browsing.
    </para>

    &lfs74_checked;

